##### Public#getmarkets()
Get the available markets

```javascript
import Bittrex from 'bittrex-api';
const bittrex = new Bittrex({});
```
```javascript
 bittrex.v1.Public.getmarkets().then((response) => {
   console.log(response);
   let data = response.result;
 }).catch((e) => {
   console.error(e);
 });
```

